rating_comment: This was the best place where I stayed during my 3 weeks in Bangladesh. Banani is nice area, there are good restaurants around, all the services at Banani are easily walkable and the area is secure. Hosts are amazing and apartment is great! This was so good that I came back before my flight away from Bangladesh!
